Izudin DUBINOVIC, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
DES MOINES PUBLIC SCHOOLS, Defendant-Appellee. No. 18-0194 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Izudin Dubinovic appeals the district court judicial review decision affirming the final agency action of the workers' compensation commissioner. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
